{"tha-ap211:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap211:0.2":"Kanikarapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap211:0.3":"Adharadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap211:1.1":"“Adharakam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap211:1.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap211:1.3":"Dharemi pathavim sabbam, ","tha-ap211:1.4":"kevalam vasudham imam. ","tha-ap211:2.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap211:2.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap211:2.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap211:2.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap211:3.1":"Sattavise ito kappe, ","tha-ap211:3.2":"ahesum caturo jana; ","tha-ap211:3.3":"Samantavarana nama, ","tha-ap211:3.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap211:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap211:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap211:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap211:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma adharadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap211:6.1":"Adharadayakattherassapadanam navamam. "}